7 (5) The department shall reimburse a utility as authorized in subsection (3) of this
8 section if the department is satisfied that the utility's facilities have been relocated
9 in conformance with the plan approved by the department. The utility shall have
10 twelve (12) months from the completion date of the relocation, according to the
11 schedule of calendar days, to submit a reimbursement request for relocation costs to
12 the department.
13 (6) The provisions of this section shall not amend or affect in any way the provisions of
14 KRS 179.265.
